Package: nycha
Title: Data on the New York City Housing Authority
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Kieran", "Healy", , "kjhealy@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides spatial and tabular data on the New York City
    Housing Authority (NYCHA), including public housing developments,
    residential addresses, the development data book, housing maintenance
    code violations on NYCHA properties, community facilities, service
    centers, and resident summary statistics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 8.0.0
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
URL: https://github.com/kjhealy/nycha
BugReports: https://github.com/kjhealy/nycha/issues
Suggests: 
    sf (>= 1.0.0),
    tibble (>= 3.0.0)
